snippet.title: Upstream | Reveal Trailer - WISHLIST NOW!
snippet.description:
Play as a salmon journeying home in this physics based, precision platformer using only two buttons! Remember that on a voyage through innumerable obstacles and constant danger, progress may not be linear. Available to wishlist now on Steam!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3245890/Upstream/ 
Website: https://gllamagames.com/ 
Discord: https://discord.gg/U9TVUuEWQA 
BlueSky: https://bsky.app/profile/gllama.games 

#videogames #indiegame #platformer #pixelart #nature #salmon
